snippet.title: AirportSim - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming October 19th on Steam: Airport Sim! - Wishlist Now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715280/AirportSim/

AirportSim is an Advanced Airport Ground Handling Simulator with true-to-life visuals and operations, licensed planes and vehicles, real airports and live weather conditions. Enjoy the many tasks alone or with friends, making this experience unforgettable.

Stay up to date with AirportSim and Iceberg Interactive: 

Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/TheAirportSim/
https://www.facebook.com/iceberginteractive

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/airport_sim
http://twitter.com/Iceberg_Int

Discord: http://discord.gg/iceberginteractive
Official website: https://airportsim.com/
Steam publisher page: http://bit.ly/IcebergOnSteam
